data.description: Welcome Home.. This complete updated and open concept home comes with all the bells and whistles. New kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, and steel appliances. This home is perfect for entertaining with two terrific living areas and original hardwood floors. if you are looking for spacious bedrooms this is definitely the home for you. The Master suite hosts a large  closet and en suite master bathroom. Need backyard space? This fully fenced in backyard is perfect. Close to Youree Drive, Line Ave, and LSUHSC this home is ready for you.
